### Create a new reply to a task
POST http://localhost:3334/api/reply HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "budget": 100,
  "comment": "Reply to the task",
  "taskId": "some-task-id",
  "userId": "some-user-id"
}

### Get a reply by ID
GET http://localhost:3334/api/reply/51599d01-9abe-4794-9345-ec720c70f042 HTTP/1.1

### Delete a reply by ID
DELETE http://localhost:3334/api/reply/51599d01-9abe-4794-9345-ec720c70f042 HTTP/1.1
